  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p689524/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201409/656774c0c36845ac951f56ee2b2b8a3f.jpg\" style=\"height: 472px; width: 460px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tActor Andy Lau has shot down rumors he's <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/feuding with\" target=\"_blank\">feuding with</a> fellow Hong Kong <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/A-lister\" target=\"_blank\">A-lister</a> Stephen Chow.刘德华已经回应他与香港明星周星驰的不和传闻。</p>\n<p>\n\tLau attended a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/premiere\" target=\"_blank\">premiere</a> for <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/documentary\" target=\"_blank\">documentary</a> &quot;My Voice, My Life&quot; in Hong Kong on Sept 12 and took the opportunity to set the record straight.9月12日，刘德华在香港出席写实电影纪录片&ldquo;争气&rdquo;的宣传活动，并借此机会澄清。</p>\n<p>\n\t&quot;First off, I never said that he is not my friend,&quot; said Lau. &quot;That's what I want to clarify. Also, about my <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/paycheck\" target=\"_blank\">paycheck</a>, these are just rumors.&quot;&ldquo;首先我没有亲口说他不是我朋友，&rdquo;刘德华说。&quot;我要澄清一下,而且，片酬那些东西都是传闻，不是事实。&rdquo;</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">Chow is one of Hong Kong's most revered comedic actors, with international hits like &quot;Shaolin Soccer&quot; (2001) and &quot;Kung Fu Hustle&quot; (2004) under his belt.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">周星驰是香港最受尊崇的喜剧演员之一，有着在国际上备受欢迎的电影</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">《少林足球》(2001)和《功夫》(2004)。</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span></p>\n<p>\n\tHis last film, &quot;Journey to the West: <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Conquering\" target=\"_blank\">Conquering</a> the Demons,&quot; was also a box office hit in China.他最近的一部电影《大话西游》，在中国的票房表现也不俗。</p>\n<p>\n\tWhen asked about his relationship with Chow, Lau said, &quot;I was, am, and will always be a fan.&quot;<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">当问及与周星驰的关系时，刘德华说：&ldquo;</span>我只可以说现在，以前，未来我都是他影迷。<span>&rdquo;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p689524/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p689524\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p658542/\">男人心声：爱素颜，不等于完全不化妆的女人</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p686070/\">凯特王妃御用设计师：平底鞋让女人更美</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p683618/\">6张图带你看懂 没有苏格兰,英国怎么办</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p679466/\">囧研究 男人不论多大都喜欢22岁以下女人</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p686802/\">谜团侦破：卷福女友大揭晓</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p677500/\">2015年考研时间已公布提前至2014年12月27-28日</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p673779/\">环眼全球：古今中外世界各地开学都啥样？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p643047/\">盘点十个那些你最喜欢的美剧中出现的谎言</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p532552/\">免费在线学：CCTalk英语大厅课程表</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" 